messages:
Name: Dominik Livakovic
Nationality: Croatia
Date of Birth: January 9, 1995
Position: Goalkeeper
Current club: Girona
LaLiga clubs played for: Girona
Girona goalkeeper Dominik Livakovic is yet to make his LaLiga debut after joining the club on September 1, 2025.
Girona next face a trip to Elche in LaLiga action on December 7.
In last season's Süper Lig, Livakovic appeared in 22 games for Fenerbahçe and clinched a clean sheet in eight of those fixtures.
Livakovic linked up with Girona on loan in September 2025 from Fenerbahçe, for whom he has made 57 league appearances in total.
